                     <handNote xml:id="h3" script="Ethiopic"> Hand b: <locus from="33r" to="64v">33r-64v</locus>, somewhat less careful than hand a; in some portions of
                        the Ms., the handrwiring is uneven.
                        <!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h4" script="Ethiopic"> Text I is written with smaller letters
                        in comparison to those of Text II. The letters of Text I gradually become
                        smaller and their size stabilizes around <locus target="#10">10</locus>.<!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#2r">2r</locus>: finely elaborate coloured (dark blue, red,
                        yellow) ornamental band with four vertical extensions reaching the bottom of
                        the text; geometric, floral and anthropomorphic motifs. A pair of ailes over
                        each image of "face".</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d2">
                        <locus target="#9v">9v</locus>: elaborate coloured (dark blue, red, yellow)
                        ornamental band with four extensions reaching the bottom of the text;
                        interlaces, geometric, floral motifs; floral, anthropomorfic and zoomorfic
                        motifs used for the decoration of the horizontal band.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d3">
                        <locus target="#49r">49r</locus>: elaborate uncoloured ornamental band with
                        four vertical extensions reaching the bottom of the page; interlaces,
                        anthropomorfic motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                        <locus target="#2vb">2vb</locus>: coloured (dark blue and yellow) ornamental
                        band; interlaces.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d5">
                        <locus target="#3vb">3vb</locus>: uncoloured ornamental band;
                        interlaces.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d6">
                        <locus target="#8vb">8vb</locus>: coloured (yellow, dark blue) ornamental
                        band; interlaces.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d7">
                        <locus target="#33ra">33ra</locus>: black ornamental band;
                        interlaces.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
